{
  "name": "Echo EDR: Network Actions Analysis",
  "cy_name": "echo_edr_network_actions_reasoning",
  "description": "Enriches alerts with Echo EDR network connection analysis. Extracts IP from device/network info, retrieves network connections, performs AI-powered behavioral analysis to identify C2 activity, data exfiltration, or lateral movement patterns. Adds structured enrichment data to alert.",
